data.description: This home is not located in the flood zone. Approx. 3000 SF LAKE HOUSE with 100’ of shore line. Home is move in READY! Kitchen includes custom cabinets, an island and oversized pantry. Master bedroom is downstairs with a large closet , jacuzzi tub and stand alone shower. Closet measures 12X9 with built in drawers and shelves. Living room was expanded after original construction adding a fireplace and windows. Upstairs offers two bedrooms, Jack and Jill bathroom with a claw foot tub. Yard has 50+ trees, raised beds and plenty of room to play. Covered porch with built in benches and ceiling fans. Two storage buildings with covered parking for a boat. All measurements to be verified by buyer before closing.
